      ],
      "phase_evolution": "Mn and C partition from both α-ferrite and δ-ferrite to austenite; Si partitions from austenite to δ-ferrite and α-ferrite. These partitioning effects influence austenite stability and explain the discrepancy between observed and equilibrium-predicted austenite fractions."
